pan></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Simp.Simproc</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.expandDiv","kind":"def","line":63,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.expandDiv","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.lean#L63-L74"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.expandPow01\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">expandPow01</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.Simproc\">Simp.Simproc</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Applies `a^0 = 1`, `a^1 = a`.\n\nWe do normalize `a^0` and `a^1` when converting expressions into polynomials,\nbut we need to normalize them here when for other preprocessing steps such as\n`a / b = a*b⁻¹`. If `b` is of the form `c^1`, it will be treated as an\natom in the ring module.\n\n**Note**: We used to expand `a^(n+m)` here, but it prevented `grind` from solving\nsimple problems such as\n```\nexample {k : Nat} (h : k - 1 + 1 = k) :\n    2 ^ (k - 1 + 1) = 2 ^ k := by\n  grind\n```\nWe now use a propagator for `a^(n+m)` which adds the `a^n*a^m` to the equivalence class.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.expandPow01","kind":"def","line":22,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.expandPow01","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.lean#L22-L54"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.mkSemiringThm\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">Arith</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSemiringThm</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.mkSemiringThm","kind":"def","line":16,"name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.Arith.mkSemiringThm","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/9d4ad1273f6cea397c3066c2c83062a4410d16bf/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Arith/Simproc.lean#L16-L20"}}],"imports":["Init.Grind.Ring.Basic","Init.Simproc","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Simp.Simproc","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.SynthInstance","Init.Grind.Ring.Field"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Arith.Simproc"}